1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,500
Meet Punch, the baby snow monkey from
Ichikawa City Zoo in Japan.

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:09,500
After his mother rejected him,
keepers gave him a giant orangutan plush.

3
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:14,800
Videos of Punch hugging and carrying it
went viral worldwide.

4
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:22,000
Now he is slowly building confidence
and starting to socialize with other monkeys.
